			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Just so people can learn from my stupid mistake. I already had quested a pair of gauntlets for myself. Then I came across another avocet, killed it, and got another charm. So I said, what the heck, I'll do the quest again, get the exp and sell the gauntlets for a small profit. Didn't notice that these are LORE! *sigh*  Gave the gem and charm to centaur, go the exp, he says here you go, but look! Nowhere in my inventory! DOH!<BR>
<BR>
So learn from my silly mistake. If you want to do this quest repeatedly, sell your current gauntlets first, then turn in charm for new ones. Silly trollie. :)<BR>
<BR>
Toreck, Level 32 Troll Warrior
				</font>
